schools.name: Charles J. Colgan Sr. High School

data.description: Beautiful and affordable 5 bedroom home with 4.25% assumable loan situated in amenity rich Meadowbrook Woods community and routed to coveted Colgan High and award winning elementary and middle schools. Lovingly updated with brand new neutral paint, modern lighting fixtures, energy saving stainless steel appliances, sturdy new water heater, shiny bathroom fixtures, privacy blinds and shades and luxury plank flooring throughout. Step inside your welcoming foyer that is adjoined by a private home office with French doors and a formal living room that flows to your separate dining room surrounded by chairralling and crown molding and makes a perfect spot for entertaining friends and family with meals made in your spacious kitchen offering ample cabinets and counter space, tiled backsplash, recessed lighting, a full pantry, an oversized island and a breakfast bar for those days you are eating on the go.  Alongside of the kitchen you have a sunroom with a vaulted ceiling and a wall of windows overlooking your gorgeously manicured yard with a tree lined view that creates an intimate entertaining area on the large deck. The relaxing family room features floor to ceiling windows that allow an abundance of natural light during the day and a cozy gas fireplace to enjoy on crisp evenings. Start your day in a generously sized primary bedroom with private En-Suite  including dual sinks, spa tub, standing shower and a water closet. Four additional bedrooms on the upper level and a second full bath provide space and serenity for all. Make this house your home today!
